summary: I just can't stop crying today. It's one year since I had the best day of my life, since I heard reputation the first time, had...
body: I just can’t stop crying today. It’s one year since I had the best day of my life, since I heard reputation the first time, had my arms wrapped around Taylor and got internet friends for life (+it was the first time I met @taylorsparklingswift and we’re best friends now). I’m so emotional! And happy. And thankful. And wow it’s just such a special feeling.
